@startuml remove-entry-activity
title RemoveEntryUseCase - Activity

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1976D2
}

start
:Input:\nvaultId, entryId;
:Source:\npackages/core/src/use-cases/vault-entries/remove-entry.ts;
:Require unlocked vault context for "remove entry";
:Check active entry exists;
if (entry missing?) then (yes)
  :Throw PasswordEntryNotFoundError;
  stop
endif
:Prepare local mutation with VaultSyncGuardService;
:Get deletion timestamp from ClockPort;
:Build updated unlocked vault with removePasswordEntryFromVault;
note right
The domain mutation creates a deleted-entry tombstone
and advances version vectors for the current device.
end note
:Persist updated vault as signed local snapshot;
if (syncConfig exists?) then (yes)
  :Require saved local snapshot;
  :Upload persisted local mutation through sync guard;
endif
:Commit persisted snapshot vector to unlocked session;
:Return entryId, snapshotVersionVector, revisionTimestamp;
stop
@enduml
